Title: Hazardous Horticulture
Description:
We may be outnumbered, but this is my domain. And I have a way of evening our odds.

Take this pouch of seeds. Plant them throughout Wildfire Canyon and the Dream's faerie dragons will transform them into treants.

With luck, they will draw attention from our front lines and bolster our ground forces.
ObjectivesText: Plant 6 Dream Seeds across Wildfire Canyon.
